data.name: 0000 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We're gonna head off to keep lookout at the music room now.

data.name: 0001 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Thankfully, that little sister of mine's gone off with Haruhi and left me in peace.

data.name: 0002 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: There's plenty I'd like to confirm while we still have the opportunity.

data.name: 0003 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Remember how that Computer Society member was acting just now?

data.name: 0004 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Indeed. I wouldn't hesitate to call that unusual for even a second.

data.name: 0005 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I expect you may have noticed something—isn't that right, Miss Nagato?

data.name: 0006 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Is that true?

data.name: 0009 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It doesn't matter what it is—tell us, Nagato.

data.name: 0010 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: That club member was programmed to carry out some form of objective.

data.name: 0011 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: For what? Who would do such a thing?

data.name: 0012 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: The objective is unclear. All data is lacking at the present.

data.name: 0013 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Do you know who did it?

data.name: 0014 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: That is also unclear.

data.name: 0015 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: It can be estimated that they possess a certain degree of data manipulating ability.

data.name: 0016 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Data manipulation, huh…? For example?

data.name: 0017 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: A similar existence to that of a data lifeform. …That and…

data.name: 0018 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What?

data.name: 0019 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Nagato herself, perhaps? An equivalent being would also be possible.

data.name: 0020 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What are you trying to say, Koizumi?

data.name: 0021 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Surely you're not trying to say Nagato did it, right?

data.name: 0022 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'm not saying it was Nagato, or thinking it was Nagato.

data.name: 0023 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Itsuki Koizumi's statement is… valid.

data.name: 0024 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: It would be possible for a being of my capabilities or greater.

data.name: 0025 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Hey, Nagato, I don't get why you're saying something so not worth mentioning…

data.name: 0026 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You don't have to go out of your way to raise suspicion of yourself, right?

data.name: 0027 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: But, it's true.

data.name: 0028 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, maybe… but…

data.name: 0029 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: All you have to say at a time like this is "it wasn't me."

data.name: 0030 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: And while you're at it, complain about that guy who just said something very rude…

data.name: 0031 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Complain?

data.name: 0032 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: There's a lot to complain about, right?

data.name: 0033 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Like—"don't treat me like some criminal."

data.name: 0034 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Or maybe—"your smile is gross."

data.name: 0035 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I think that's more what you're thinking, rather than Miss Nagato.

data.name: 0036 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Oops, I accidentally let my feelings slip there…

data.name: 0037 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey, don't treat Nagato like a criminal.

data.name: 0038 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Even if she said something like that herself.

data.name: 0039 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'm sorry.

data.name: 0040 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I was only intending to raise an objective fact.

data.name: 0041 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It's never my intention to be insensitive.

data.name: 0042 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I know I'm making this claim myself, but…

data.name: 0043 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: …most of the time, I believe I'm saying the right thing.

data.name: 0044 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Good grief… That's some excessive self-confidence.

data.name: 0045 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So the only thing we know is that we don't know who did it, huh…

data.name: 0046 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I wouldn't go that far.

data.name: 0047 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What do you mean?

data.name: 0048 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: At the very least, that guy must've come in contact with the true culprit.

data.name: 0049 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: If we ask him, might we not at least be able to get some kind of lead?

data.name: 0050 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I see. If we ask the guy himself, that'd be pretty efficient.

data.name: 0051 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Alright—change of course then. Let's head to the Computer Society clubroom.

data.name: 0054 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Oh, what? There's no one here? We must've passed them.

data.name: 0055 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Take a look at this.

data.name: 0056 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: This is what the club member was frantically writing earlier.

data.name: 0057 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It's sheet music? There's loads.

data.name: 0058 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: If we examine this more closely, we may be able to figure something out.

data.name: 0059 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What should we do? Borrow the sheet music?

data.name: 0060 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: This is an important clue. We should borrow it.

data.name: 0061 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It'd be a pain if taking this out at our own leisure becomes a problem later.

data.name: 0062 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's leave it here.

data.name: 0063 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I wonder if we can't backup any suspicious data.

data.name: 0064 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I guess if we copy it, we won't have to remove the original…

data.name: 0065 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's borrow one of these unused disks.

data.name: 0066 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Maybe that club member went home?

data.name: 0067 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: There's no way to confirm where he went if there's no one here.

data.name: 0068 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: For the time being, let's head to the music room as we planned originally.

data.name: 0071 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey, aren't you from the Computer Socie…

data.name: 0072 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Hold on for a moment. Something seems strange about him.

data.name: 0073 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He's holding something. What is… that?

data.name: 0074 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It looks like he's placing some sort of box in the corridor.

data.name: 0075 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Music box.

data.name: 0076 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What did you say? Is that the thing he's holding?

data.name: 0077 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Yes.

data.name: 0078 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Let's just try talking to him. Hey, mind if we ask you some questions?

data.name: 0079 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Don't interrupt me—!

data.name: 0080 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Wha—?! What's dangerous!

data.name: 0081 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Be careful! He's out of his mind!

data.name: 0082 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: If you're gonna interrupt me…

data.name: 0083 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Waaaaaaah!!

data.name: 0084 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: O-oi! Slow down!

data.name: 0085 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Ah…

data.name: 0087 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato held her hand over the forehead of the club member as he attacked me…

data.name: 0088 (399.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …the moment she did, he fell to the floor as if losing consciousness.

data.name: 0089 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What did you just do, Nagato?

data.name: 0090 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I deleted the behavioral program.

data.name: 0091 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: That was a close one.

data.name: 0092 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It appears he was being controlled by the behavioral program.

data.name: 0093 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: H-huh? Why am I here…?

data.name: 0094 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You don't remember?

data.name: 0095 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Wha…?! Huh…?! SOS Brigade?!

data.name: 0096 (399.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Prez told me not to get involved with the SOS Brigade—I mean, I'm busy so I've got to go!

data.name: 0098 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's up with that?

data.name: 0099 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It seems he has no memories of when he was under the control of the behavioral program.

data.name: 0100 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: For his sake, I believe that most likely to be a good thing.

data.name: 0101 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I guess we were unable to interview him then. Well, what can you do.

data.name: 0102 (399.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Here.

data.name: 0103 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's this? Ah, the music box he was holding, right?

data.name: 0104 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh, I won't make any noise… Maybe it broke when it was dropped?

data.name: 0105 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: He was trying to plant this thing here, right?

data.name: 0106 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I get the feeling it'd be dangerous to leave this here.

data.name: 0107 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I'll keep hold of it.

data.name: 0108 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: There's not really much that can be done if it's broken. I'll leave it here.

data.name: 0109 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: There's something on the floor… That club member's student handbook?

data.name: 0110 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I don't think there's any need for him to dislike the SOS Brigade as much as he does.

data.name: 0111 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, I don't think there's any hope if you want to amend that.

data.name: 0112 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I'll get this back to him later…

data.name: 0113 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: In the end, some inexplicable thing is trying to do something inexplicable…

data.name: 0114 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …it seems.

data.name: 0115 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It certainly seems that way.

data.name: 0116 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: What should we do?

data.name: 0117 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Whatever we do, we have to do it before Haruhi finds out.

data.name: 0118 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That's for sure.

data.name: 0119 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: I'm of the absolute same opinion. We really think alike.

data.name: 0120 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Don't look so pleased when you say that…

data.name: 0121 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: For now, let's meet up with Miss Asahina and the others.

data.name: 0122 (399.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: They may have figured something out.

data.name: 0123 (399.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Good point. Let's go then.

data.name: 0124 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Warn Nagato

data.name: 0125 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Complain to Koizumi

data.name: 0126 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Borrow the sheet music

data.name: 0127 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Leave it alone

data.name: 0128 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Take the music box

data.name: 0129 (399.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Don't need the music box
